124
00:06:16,590 --> 00:06:17,270
The door is right there.

125
00:06:17,830 --> 00:06:19,320
You can walk out now.

126
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:20,880
Baixiao Sect

127
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,960
