134
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,270
Lord Bai, Xiao Chong,

135
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:50,520
and Lord Chi, Xiao Yu.

136
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,150
Interesting.

137
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,150
