138
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:58,960
I don't think

139
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,640
Lord Yong'an has any reason to help me.

140
00:07:02,350 --> 00:07:03,880
If he sees me now,

141
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,230
