will be kept confidential,

233
00:10:58,590 --> 00:11:00,510
you've got

234
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,510
a lot of nerves.

235
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:08,230
I never intend

236
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:09,230
to hide my identity.

237
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:11,400
