266
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:37,510
I can give you more.

267
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:39,920
As long as

268
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:43,920
you give me the list,

269
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:46,960
