278
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:22,510
Eunuchs,

279
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,710
you both made the wrong choice.

280
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,680
There are

281
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:29,710
